    "bookShortLabel": "7下",
    "bookOrder": 251,
    "summary": "借死海、马达加斯加雨林与冰川的第一人称“呼救”，理解生态危机。"
  },
  "sentences": [
    {
      "id": "u13-article-s1",
      "text": "I’m not a sea but a lake.",
      "paragraphId": "u13-article-p1",
      "tr": "我不是海，而是一个湖。",
      "g": "主语 + 系动词 + 表语",
      "d": "not...but... 意为“不是...而是...”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/YZTZdJuX2Zf64bjJujbaU5.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u13-article-s2",
      "text": "And I’m not dead.",
      "paragraphId": "u13-article-p1",
      "tr": "而且我并没有死。",
      "g": "主语 + 系动词 + 表语",
      "d": "dead 是形容词，作表语。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/buaZXxa8YBkmfDAUU5tKMB.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u13-article-s3",
      "text": "In fact, I’ve got many plants and animals.",
      "paragraphId": "u13-article-p1",
      "tr": "事实上，我有许多植物和动物。",
      "g": "现在完成时",
      "d": "In fact 意为“事实上”；have got 意为“有”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/3PCbFqC3YiHQtLJjAi46fG.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u13-article-s4",
      "text": "I’m saltier than any sea, so people can lie on my surface.",
      "paragraphId": "u13-article-p1",
      "tr": "我比任何海洋都咸，所以人们可以躺在我的水面上。",
      "g": "比较级",
      "d": "saltier 是 salty 的比较级；than any... 比任何...都...。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/8oFVu4M2GdPXdMjGcfzfnY.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u13-article-s5",
      "text": "Rivers flow into me.",
      "paragraphId": "u13-article-p1",
      "tr": "河流汇入我的怀抱。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语",
      "d": "flow into 意为“流进”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/h8BfNhh5Hfcq4sDbHtXvuB.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u13-article-s6",
      "text": "But now people take too much water from them.",
      "paragraphId": "u13-article-p1",
      "tr": "但现在人们从这些河流中抽取了太多的水。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 宾语",
      "d": "too much 修饰不可数名词 water。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/ChTjy9J5BKgwf4uVpRi56K.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u13-article-s7",
      "text": "My water level is going down.",
      "paragraphId": "u13-article-p1",
      "tr": "我的水位正在下降。",
      "g": "现在进行时",
      "d": "go down 意为“下降”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/frWadjuLu6GTHWNHiBmPiG.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u13-article-s8",
      "text": "I am becoming smaller year by year.",
      "paragraphId": "u13-article-p1",
      "tr": "我正在一年年变小。",
      "g": "现在进行时",
      "d": "year by year 意为“一年又一年地”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/kMmvy8SWEGXirYpnJdKy5R.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u13-article-s9",
      "text": "Take less water, or I’ll dry up within the next 100 years.",
      "paragraphId": "u13-article-p1",
      "tr": "少用点水，否则我将在未来100年内干涸。",
      "g": "祈使句 + or",
      "d": "祈使句 + or... 意为“做...，否则...”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/tD8UbDEppB7dREHQeRhNPV.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u13-article-s10",
      "text": "Then I really will be dead!",
      "paragraphId": "u13-article-p1",
      "tr": "到那时我就真的死了！",
      "g": "一般将来时",
      "d": "really 副词修饰动词 will be。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/vLveKEiPnVEtfbPoyVS94R.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u13-article-s11",
      "text": "I’m the rainforest of Madagascar.",
      "paragraphId": "u13-article-p2",
      "tr": "我是马达加斯加的雨林。",
      "g": "主语 + 系动词 + 表语",
      "d": "rainforest 意为“雨林”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/PvoPVAw2ytogTf7XLPNfkL.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u13-article-s12",
      "text": "As my name suggests, I make rain for my plants and animals, such as monkeys, snakes and many kinds of flowers.",
      "paragraphId": "u13-article-p2",
      "tr": "正如我的名字所暗示的，我为我的动植物制造雨水，比如猴子、蛇和许多种花。",
      "g": "复合句",
      "d": "As...suggests 正如...所暗示；such as 意为“例如”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/6VttDJSiXb7YqRG4TiSTSS.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u13-article-s13",
      "text": "For 80% of them, I’m their only home in the world.",
      "paragraphId": "u13-article-p2",
      "tr": "对于它们中80%的生物来说，我是它们在世界上唯一的家。",
      "g": "主语 + 系动词 + 表语",
      "d": "only 意为“唯一的”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/HiFFgds627C85cvf9hJQA6.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u13-article-s14",
      "text": "However, people are cutting down my trees for wood and to make space for farming.",
      "paragraphId": "u13-article-p2",
      "tr": "然而，人们为了木材和开垦农田正在砍伐我的树木。",
      "g": "现在进行时",
      "d": "cut down 意为“砍倒”；make space for 为...腾出空间。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/jUEFEEzyAZNLUFUUpzZ4Hm.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u13-article-s15",
      "text": "Please stop it.",
      "paragraphId": "u13-article-p2",
      "tr": "请停止这种行为。",
      "g": "祈使句",
      "d": "stop doing sth. 停止做某事。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/UzMgPdYeRi5upxgyahPUY4.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u13-article-s16",
      "text": "I’m disappearing.",
      "paragraphId": "u13-article-p2",
      "tr": "我正在消失。",
      "g": "现在进行时",
      "d": "disappear 意为“消失”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/cELPxByFGQXrUPRMGENuMf.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u13-article-s17",
      "text": "I’m a glacier at the Glacier National Park in America.",
      "paragraphId": "u13-article-p3",
      "tr": "我是美国冰川国家公园的一座冰川。",
      "g": "主语 + 系动词 + 表语",
      "d": "glacier 意为“冰川”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/ztL7S9vUcDTnQesqgKLvBH.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u13-article-s18",
      "text": "It’s a land full of ice and snow.",
      "paragraphId": "u13-article-p3",
      "tr": "这是一片充满冰雪的土地。",
      "g": "主语 + 系动词 + 表语",
      "d": "full of 意为“充满”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/B5LHVNCP8c8mHaMjb8JP7E.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u13-article-s19",
      "text": "Do you want to explore the white world in the film *Frozen*?",
      "paragraphId": "u13-article-p3",
      "tr": "你想探索电影《冰雪奇缘》中的白色世界吗？",
      "g": "一般疑问句",
      "d": "want to do sth. 想要做某事；explore 意为“探索”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/E43vJe997d9HEoRsmAZouF.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u13-article-s20",
      "text": "Then my home is the best choice.",
      "paragraphId": "u13-article-p3",
      "tr": "那么我的家就是最好的选择。",
      "g": "主语 + 系动词 + 表语",
      "d": "best choice 意为“最好的选择”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/cZPYiEtgPrXj64Ry8XxfVQ.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u13-article-s21",
      "text": "Two hundred years ago, there were about 150 glaciers.",
      "paragraphId": "u13-article-p3",
      "tr": "两百年前，大约有150座冰川。",
      "g": "There be 结构",
      "d": "there were 是 there be 的过去式。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/vCmVGukKMumZzTCrJabDxH.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u13-article-s22",
      "text": "But now, there are around 25.",
      "paragraphId": "u13-article-p3",
      "tr": "但现在，只剩下大约25座了。",
      "g": "There be 结构",
      "d": "around 意为“大约”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/fzqAFhWyQFsYQNYaNQ7BAU.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u13-article-s23",
      "text": "Please stop climate change.",
      "paragraphId": "u13-article-p3",
      "tr": "请停止气候变化。",
      "g": "祈使句",
      "d": "climate change 意为“气候变化”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/LQqvFYcfZLnrqeDDRJyRHJ.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u13-article-s24",
      "text": "I’m turning into *Waterworld*!",
      "paragraphId": "u13-article-p3",
      "tr": "我这儿快成《水世界》了！",
      "g": "现在进行时",
      "d": "turn into 意为“变成”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/UojUeXL3qKVPHgPcU4jZAF.mp3"
    }
  ],
